original_title: 2022年2月19日 北海道・北海道立総合体育センター 北海きたえーる
overview: After a month of touring around Japan, the New Year’s Golden Series comes to a close over two nights in Sapporo’s Hokkai Kita-Yell on February 19 and 20. Three championship matches highlight Saturdays clashes with what is sure to be a classical main event.
tagline: IWGP United States heavyweight Championship: Hiroshi Tanahashi vs SANADA
title: New year’s Golden Series night 14
